						<div class="postbody">I've seen both on both sides. I think stability is directly related to overall complexity of modern software, not just paid/free.<br /><br />I'd say that free software, although sometimes pretty powerful and could compete with paid software feature-wise, is often has major usability issues. I consider it to be a price of some kind, either you pay tons of money and get comfort, or don't pay money, get abilities to do the same things, but lose extra time doing it.</div>

